desc: Small local Brisbane and Gold Coast dehydrated dog treats business providing good quality, safe, yummy and affordable dog and cat treats to pet owners across Australia. We have a large variety of pet treats including real meat jerky, biscuits, bones, liver, duck, beef, kangaroo, roo, chicken, lamb seafood & vegetarian.

layout.text: Our treats are good quality, safe, affordable and most importantly your dog will think they taste great!
